<br>
Even the names of items that drop in VP have historical refrence. <br>
<br>
The key, is fine, the steps are a joke at this stage in EQ. They became trivial to get just after SoV. Now that SOL is out they are even easier.<br>
<br>
VP is the one zone a uber guild or even not so uber guild can go to get away from other people. <br>
<br>
The point about NtOV not being keyed is true aswell. It should have been however they keyed sleepers and didnt want 2x the quest for people to complain. instead the dragons were recently made a lil more difficult. Not hard enough but harder. <br>
<br>
VP needs to be redone, so that it uses all classes to complete. Dificulty increased on all Dragons, make it so one can work through the zone instead of staying at safe points. <br>
<br>
<br>
VP to me is one of the best zones in all of EQ. most of my guild go and farm it just for the fun of it. To relive old Hosh flash backs.<br>
<br>
Phara Dar is the only 32k hp dragon I know of that can kill a guild that can clear tovN<br>
<br>
ad 100k hp to him and he would be truely epic.<br>
